# Binary game assets — mark explicitly so core.autocrlf (this repo has it ON)
# never applies CRLF normalization to them. Without this, Windows checkouts can
# show phantom "modified" diffs on binaries (or worse, corrupt them). See the
# audio-cleanup worklog: the audio .wav churn that looked like "uncommitted work".
*.wav   binary
*.ogg   binary
*.mp3   binary
*.flac  binary
*.glb   binary
*.fbx   binary
*.tga   binary
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.wasm  binary
*.ttf   binary
*.otf   binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
